strings: <se_low>January: What is the secret of the "Lapp Field"? This building, this old ship...
<se_low>January: You must be doomed! Do you want to find a lost treasure in the game Hunt for Lost Treasure?
<se_low>January: Oh, those old horns are good, aren't they? We still have a chance to get up early!
<se_low>January: But no demon can defeat us. Why is this person's situation different? then<:> "Flamin' Desu" and "Clean!"
<se_low>January: I don't believe it! The traitor Marcellus entered and said, "Help me?" I felt the wind...
<se_low>January: Well, the "e" is at the end, isn't it? It's selfish to try and get rid of the "UK tax". ... Come on, I'm out and in!
<se_low>January: The Jack O' Whatsup geyser is gone, but the place is still eerie. ...brrr, yeah that's a bit scary.
<se_high>Accuracy: What happened to this place? The weather is stifling here. With every breath I felt the darkness closing in.
<se_high>Accuracy: Okay, I'm mad now! You can't beat Albert Holo for this.
<se_high>Accuracy: Forget about this scary place! Dont worry! All I can think about right now is killing a large lamb! such as butter
<se_high>Accuracy: Is it time to go out and talk about the little things?
<se_high>Accuracy: Go back to Marcelo and help him defeat this thief!
<se_high>Accuracy: We have no reason to stay here. Because you defeated a real wizard, right?
<se_def>China: Doesn't this place look like a dark ruin? If there was a place to worship the Dark Lord, this is it.
<se_def>China: No doubt it was the perfect base for his men. very bright
<se_def>China: I'm not going to lie, the idea of retrieving a giant from a wet ditch is uncomfortable and weird...
<se_def>China: Why bother then?
<se_def>China: If you have a fever, it doesn't matter if you catch a ghost. You can also continue using the palette. I can't bear this feeling anymore...
<se_def>China: Ha ha ha... Well what we started is finished.
<se_def>China: I have ideas. Is it okay if we see each other later?
<se_high>Dye: Well, it doesn't matter if it doesn't "smell like honey". Don't worry, I'm ready.
<se_high>Dye: I don't like Jugget and his "creepy" image. Black magic works.
<se_high>Dye: Personally, I would like to give up and leave.
<se_high>Dye: Oh, I didn't expect this to happen. Who would have expected any of them to come to our aid?
<se_high>Dye: I don't know what Marcelo actually did. My friends might be my enemies, but don't worry. We are using elves.
<se_high>Dye: You have collected most items in this cave. After enjoying the scenery here, can we go out?
<se_low>It's Maurice.: Chameleon I feel alive! I'm super excited!
<se_low>It's Maurice.: ... there are a lot of new monsters that have never been seen before so hello! Isn't there a lot?
<se_low>It's Maurice.: Sea devil, this damage hunter is so cool! strong animal!
<se_low>It's Maurice.: I wish I could take her to my pool... Ha ha, but that's not gossip, is it?
<se_low>It's Maurice.: Both of them! There is no time to talk!
<se_low>It's Maurice.: First you need to return to young Fratello and defeat the devil with him. Do you remember how you used to spend time over tea and cake?
<se_low>It's Maurice.: I still don't know, the excitement is gone here.
<se_low>It's Maurice.: I feel something in my hand. I've got heavy stuff in my ears... Maybe I need a vacation, huh? i mean oh!
